            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>blanched peas</strong>,<strong> remaining chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and a splash of <strong>cold water</strong> to a pot over a medium heat</p><p>Once warm, add a large knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and mash the peas roughly</p><p>Remove the pot from the heat and stir through the juice of 1/4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1/2]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> – these are your<strong> chilli mushy peas</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
